---
const problems = [
  {
    number: '01',
    title: 'Información dispersa',
    text: 'Ventas, inventario, clientes y reportes repartidos entre Excel, WhatsApp, libretas o sistemas que no se comunican.'
  },
  {
    number: '02',
    title: 'Procesos manuales',
    text: 'Tareas repetitivas que consumen tiempo, dependen de una persona y aumentan el riesgo de errores.'
  },
  {
    number: '03',
    title: 'Poca visibilidad',
    text: 'Decisiones tomadas sin reportes claros, sin métricas actualizadas y sin una vista real de la operación.'
  },
  {
    number: '04',
    title: 'Crecimiento desordenado',
    text: 'El negocio crece, pero las herramientas no escalan al mismo ritmo y empiezan los cuellos de botella.'
  }
];
---

<section class="stats-media source-container reveal">
  <div class="problem-panel">
    <div class="problem-heading">
      <span>Problemas que resolvemos</span>

      <h2>
        Cuando tu negocio crece, operar con herramientas improvisadas empieza a costar caro.
      </h2>

      <p>
        ADNOVA ayuda a convertir procesos dispersos en sistemas claros, conectados
        y fáciles de usar para que tu equipo trabaje con más orden y menos fricción.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="problem-grid">
      {problems.map((problem, index) => (
        <article class="problem-card stagger-item" style={`--i:${index}`}>
          <span class="problem-number">{problem.number}</span>
          <div>
            <h3>{problem.title}</h3>
            <p>{problem.text}</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="video-panel reveal-image">
    <video autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata">
      <source src="/videos/programador_escribiendo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      Tu navegador no soporta video HTML5.
    </video>

    <div class="video-overlay">
      <span>Operación digital</span>
      <strong>Del desorden operativo a sistemas que conectan tu negocio.</strong>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .stats-media {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .problem-panel {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .problem-heading {
    padding: 48px 34px 44px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .problem-heading > span {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    color: var(--blue);
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: var(--weight-strong);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .problem-heading > span::before {
    content: "";
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--blue);
  }

  .problem-heading h2 {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 24px 0 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: clamp(34px, 3.8vw, 64px);
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: var(--weight-heading);
    letter-spacing: -0.068em;
  }

  .problem-heading p {
    max-width: 660px;
    margin: 24px 0 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.18vw, 19px);
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-weight: var(--weight-body);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  }

  .problem-card {
    min-height: 245px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 34px;
    padding: 30px 34px;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: var(--bg);
    transition:
      background 0.35s ease,
      color 0.35s ease,
      transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(.16, 1, .3, 1);
  }

  .problem-card:nth-child(2),
  .problem-card:nth-child(4) {
    border-right: 0;
  }

  .problem-card:nth-child(3),
  .problem-card:nth-child(4) {
    border-bottom: 0;
  }

  .problem-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    background: var(--black);
    color: white;
  }

  .problem-number {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: var(--weight-strong);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .problem-card:hover .problem-number {
    color: #9fb6ff;
  }

  .problem-card h3 {
    margin: 0;
    color: currentColor;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 2.1vw, 36px);
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: var(--weight-heading);
    letter-spacing: -0.058em;
  }

  .problem-card p {
    max-width: 360px;
    margin: 16px 0 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.45;
    font-weight: var(--weight-body);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .problem-card:hover p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
  }

  .video-panel {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 720px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--panel);
  }

  .video-panel video {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 720px;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
    filter: saturate(0.9) contrast(1.04);
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }

  .video-panel::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(
        180deg,
        rgba(8, 11, 25, 0.04) 0%,
        rgba(8, 11, 25, 0.18) 50%,
        rgba(8, 11, 25, 0.62) 100%
      );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .video-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    left: 34px;
    right: 34px;
    bottom: 34px;
    z-index: 2;
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
    color: white;
  }

  .video-overlay span {
    width: fit-content;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: var(--weight-strong);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .video-overlay span::before {
    content: "";
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--blue);
  }

  .video-overlay strong {
    max-width: 560px;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 52px);
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: var(--weight-heading);
    letter-spacing: -0.065em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .stats-media {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .problem-panel {
      border-right: 0;
    }

    .video-panel {
      min-height: 520px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .video-panel video {
      min-height: 520px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .stats-media {
      border-left: 0;
      border-right: 0;
    }

    .problem-heading {
      padding: 42px 20px 36px;
    }

    .problem-heading h2 {
      font-size: clamp(32px, 8.8vw, 46px);
      line-height: 1.03;
    }

    .problem-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .problem-card {
      min-height: 220px;
      padding: 28px 20px;
      border-right: 0 !important;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line) !important;
    }

    .problem-card:nth-child(4) {
      border-bottom: 0 !important;
    }

    .problem-card h3 {
      font-size: clamp(28px, 8vw, 40px);
    }

    .problem-card p {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .video-panel {
      min-height: 380px;
    }

    .video-panel video {
      min-height: 380px;
    }

    .video-overlay {
      left: 20px;
      right: 20px;
      bottom: 24px;
    }

    .video-overlay strong {
      font-size: clamp(28px, 8vw, 40px);
    }
  }
</style>